wn ? right ?<br>
<br>
If we are raiding FG and happened to have a few cleric interested in party in killing Ragefire (if he is up), what is politicaaly correct path ? I know FG doesn't include Nagafen, so we don't touch Nag, but what about Ragefire ? <br>
